              Hi&nbsp;<%= @user.username %>,
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 10px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.6;">
              The first month of the new year has already almost passed. How has it started for you? I would like to help to make it an awesome year for you.
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 10px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.6;">
              A year in which you stick to your resolutions or priorities and take action. So far, the most popular topics on Rakepage are related to health and fitness (well, who's not into that in the beginning of the year?), learning languages and productivity in general.
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 10px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.6;">
              These topics are predestinated for building habits of taking action on a daily basis. I built and use Rakepage to get updated without distractions, and to have an accountability system to stay motiviated and focused on progress.
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 10px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.6;">
              I continuously implement improvements based on user feedback. It would be great if you take some time to check out the latest.
            </p>

            <p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 10px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.6;">
              Here are some of the new or better features:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 6px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.4;">
                New startpage with an overview of your action metrics
              </li>
              <li style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 6px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.4;">
                Easy to define actions (no mandatory weblink is needed anymore)
              </li>
              <li style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 6px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.4;">
                General overhaul for better navigation and interaction
              </li>
            </ul>
            <br>
            <p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 10px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.6;">
              I'm eager to create a helpful tool not only for me but also for you. A short reply to this email with your feedback how I can make Rakepage awesome for you would be very helpful.
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom: 10px;font-weight: normal;font-size: 12px;line-height: 1.6;">
